---
layout: base.njk
title: Forgotten Industries
description: An archive and evidence-based memoir that explores what happens to the things we leave behind; abandoned places, unfinished projects, deserted machines, and the parts of ourselves we once thought lost.
canonical: https://forgotten-industries.net/
---

<section class="masthead">
  <div class="section-inner masthead-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="section-label">Archive & evidence-based memoir / established MMXIV</p>
      <h1>{{ site.name }}</h1>
      <p class="tagline">{{ site.tagline }}</p>
    </div>
    <img class="hero-image" src="/assets/forgotten-industries.jpeg" alt="Forgotten Industries logo, EST MMXIV">
  </div>
</section>

<section class="mirror-band" aria-labelledby="mirror-heading">
  <div class="section-inner band-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="section-label">Figure 1</p>
      <h2 id="mirror-heading">Signal clean. Domain and source remain one record.</h2>
    </div>

    <div>
      <dl class="ledger">
        <div>
          <dt>Canonical domain</dt>
          <dd><a href="{{ site.domainUrl }}">{{ site.domainHost }}</a></dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt>GitHub source</dt>
          <dd><a href="{{ site.githubUrl }}" data-track="outbound-github">{{ site.repository }}</a></dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt>Static site generator</dt>
          <dd><a href="https://www.11ty.dev/" data-track="outbound-eleventy">Eleventy</a></dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt>Contact</dt>
          <dd><a href="mailto:{{ site.contact }}" data-track="contact-email">{{ site.contact }}</a></dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt>Matthew Marx / Live Feed</dt>
          <dd><a href="https://bsky.app/profile/forgotten-industry.bsky.social" data-track="outbound-bluesky">Bluesky field signal</a></dd>
        </div>
      </dl>

      <div class="stats" aria-label="Archive counts">
        <div class="stat">
          <strong>{{ archive.projects | count }}</strong>
          <span>Projects</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <strong>{{ archive.inventory | count }}</strong>
          <span>Inventory records</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <strong>{{ archive.fieldLogs | count }}</strong>
          <span>Field logs</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <strong>{{ archive.socialPosts | count }}</strong>
          <span>Social evidence</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

