  </div>
</section>

<section class="source-band" aria-labelledby="field-notes-heading">
  <div class="section-inner band-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="section-label">Field Notes</p>
      <h2 id="field-notes-heading">A continuity channel for the archive.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="callout">
      <h3>Subscribe</h3>
      <p>Short dispatches from the bench: restoration logs, evidence finds, measurements, recovered posts, and notes that do not need a full dossier yet.</p>
      <p class="action-row"><a href="{{ site.fieldNotesSubscribeUrl }}" data-track="subscribe-field-notes">Subscribe to Field Notes</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="source-band" aria-labelledby="shelves-heading">
